description: This file defines a Java class 'FundTransferResponse' which serves as a Data Transfer Object (DTO) for conveying response data related to fund transfer operations in an internet banking microservices project. It uses Lombok annotations to generate boilerplate code for getters, setters, and builder pattern.

classes.name: FundTransferResponse
classes.description: A DTO class encapsulating the response message and transaction ID for a fund transfer operation.
